## 6.1 计算表：平台维度表

| Display Folder | Base Metrics / Dimensions |
|----------------|--------------------------|

```dax
// ========================================
// 计算表: D_Dcom-Platform Performance_Platform_Dim
// 用途: 创建平台维度表，定义各电商平台及其层级关系
// 依赖: 无（静态数据）
// 作者: Gutao | 日期: 2026-03-12
// ========================================
D_Dcom-Platform Performance_Platform_Dim = 
DATATABLE(
    "Platform_Code", STRING,
    "Platform_Name", STRING,
    "Sort_Order", INTEGER,
    "Parent_Platform", STRING,
    "Is_Total", BOOLEAN,
    "Platform_Level", INTEGER,
    {
        // Level 1 - 总计行
        {"Total", "Total", 1, "", TRUE, 1},
        
        // Level 2 - 主要平台
        {"TM", "TM", 2, "Total", FALSE, 2},
        {"JD", "JD", 3, "Total", FALSE, 2},
        
        // Level 2 - DY 汇总平台
        {"DY", "DY", 5, "Total", FALSE, 2},
        
        // Level 3 - DY 子平台
        {"DY_Family", "DY Family", 6, "DY", FALSE, 3},
        {"DY_W", "DY W", 7, "DY", FALSE, 3},
        
        // Level 2 - 其他平台
        {"RLE", "RLE", 8, "Total", FALSE, 2}
    }
)
```

### 平台层级结构
```
Total (Level 1)
├── TM        (Level 2)
├── JD        (Level 2)
├── DY        (Level 2, 汇总 = DY_Family + DY_W)
│   ├── DY Family  (Level 3)
│   └── DY W       (Level 3)
└── RLE       (Level 2)
```


