## 6.3 度量值：动态路由主入口（DDPP_Dynamic_Metric_Value_Optimized）

| Display Folder | Formatting / Dynamic Metrics |
|----------------|------------------------------|

```dax
// ========================================
// 度量值: DDPP_Dynamic_Metric_Value_Optimized
// 用途: 动态度量值路由主入口，根据平台和指标上下文
//       路由到对应的计算逻辑
// 依赖: [DDPP_DY_Platform_Router], [DDPP_Measure_Router_NonDY]
//       'D_Dcom-Platform Performance_Platform_Dim'[Platform_Code]
//       'D_Dcom-Platform Performance_Metrics_Dim'[R1Name], [R2Name]
// 作者: Gutao | 日期: 2026-03-12
// ========================================
DDPP_Dynamic_Metric_Value_Optimized = 
    VAR __SelPlatform = 
        SELECTEDVALUE(
            'D_Dcom-Platform Performance_Platform_Dim'[Platform_Code]
        )
    RETURN
        SWITCH(
            TRUE(),
            // DY 汇总平台 → 使用 DY 专用路由（汇总 DY_Family + DY_W）
            __SelPlatform = "DY",
                [DDPP_DY_Platform_Router],
            // 所有其他平台（含 DY_Family、DY_W 子平台）→ 使用通用路由
            [DDPP_Measure_Router_NonDY]
        )
```

### 路由逻辑说明
```
Platform_Code 选择
    ├── "DY"           → [DDPP_DY_Platform_Router]  (汇总 DY_Family + DY_W)
    ├── "DY_Family"    → [DDPP_Measure_Router_NonDY] (platform="DY", store="DY_Family")
    ├── "DY_W"         → [DDPP_Measure_Router_NonDY] (platform="DY", store="DY_W")
    ├── "Total"        → [DDPP_Measure_Router_NonDY] (platform="Total")
    ├── "TM"           → [DDPP_Measure_Router_NonDY] (platform="TM")
    ├── "JD"           → [DDPP_Measure_Router_NonDY] (platform="JD")
    └── "RLE"          → [DDPP_Measure_Router_NonDY] (platform="RLE")
```


